Party Other Companion Dies
    Events
        Unit - A unit Dies
    Conditions
        ((Triggering unit) is in Companion_Group.) Equal to True
        ((Triggering unit) is A Hero) Not equal to True
        (Triggering unit) Not equal to Valeria
        (Triggering unit) Not equal to Aradion
    Actions
        Unit Group - Remove (Triggering unit) from Companion_Group.
        Set VariableSet CompanionUnitKicked = (Triggering unit)
        Set VariableSet UnitHider_ReferenceUnits[(Custom value of (Triggering unit))] = (Triggering unit)
        Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Remove Companion <gen> (checking conditions)
